com.kontakt.sdk.android.common.model

Class ResolvedId

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.kontakt.sdk.android.common.model.ResolvedId
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class ResolvedId
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    This class is a connection between device ID in Eddystone (namespace:instanceId) or iBeacon (proximity:major:minor) format and an unique ID of Device object. It can be useful while resolving shuffled devices.
    See Also:
